## Opis

Threat Intelligence Platform je enterprise-grade platforma za zbiranje, analizo in distribucijo obveščevalnih podatkov o grožnjah, vključno s STIX/TAXII integracijo, threat feeds, IOC management in attribution analysis.

## Vključene komponente

### Threat Feeds Integration
- STIX/TAXII 2.1
- Commercial threat feeds
- Government threat feeds
- Open source feeds
- Dark web monitoring

### IOC Management
- IOC ingestion
- IOC enrichment
- IOC correlation
- IOC aging/expiration
- IOC distribution

### Attribution Analysis
- Threat actor profiling
- TTP analysis
- Campaign correlation
- Infrastructure mapping
- Motivation assessment

### Threat Landscape
- Industry-specific threats
- Geographic threats
- Emerging threats
- Trend analysis
- Risk scoring

### Intelligence Sharing
- ISAC integration
- Partner sharing
- Automated distribution
- Access control
- Audit logging

